SE RI PAK:  Right.  Well, I for sure, 1998, I mean I was first time in England for first year.  And after I played in, of course I want to win the tournament somehow, some reason, I don't know why.  But I played so bad.  And at the same time just kind of everything is for me is really hard time that moment.  So I don't want to come back because I don't know.  But now this tournament is a major, so I was thinking, this is going to be the one to be have the major for my collection, actually.  Yeah, it was.  And well, I just, I just really didn't expect this week.  So many good players on the top.  And I just kind of a little slow play.  And I wasn't doing well this week.  But right now I'm the last person talking in the media center, got a trophy.  That is like huge difference.  
 
SE RI PAK:  Well, first day I think almost like two, two rounds kind of pretty much was in the rain.  So first round, around 12, 13 holes of rain.  And second, third round, yesterday, around like four or five holes in the rain.  So pretty much like one, one and a half, yeah.  I think. 
 
